      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-6"><h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Decorative Boulders</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Accent pieces and focal points that anchor a xeriscape design. Placed by machine, positioned by eye.</p></div>
